Message: hi, how to create a video ad in NewsBreak

Hey there! To create a video ad in NewsBreak, you can follow these steps: 1. Go to the Ads Manager. 2. Click on 'Create Ad' and select 'Video Ad'. 3. Upload your video and fill in the required details like targeting options. 4. Save and wait for approval! You'll get notified when your ad is live. If you need more detailed guidance, check out this article: [How to create a video ad](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/19294845964045-How-to-create-a-video-ad).
